To change the color of the popup list of a page item in Oracle APEX using JavaScript, you can use the following code:

```javascript
// Get the HTML element of the page item
var pageItem = apex.item("P1_ITEM_NAME").element;

// Change the background color of the popup list
pageItem.style.backgroundColor = "red"; // Replace "red" with your desired color
```

Make sure to replace "P1_ITEM_NAME" with the actual name of your page item.

You can place this code in a Dynamic Action in Oracle APEX to trigger the JavaScript when a certain event occurs, such as page load or button click.
